{"parentUuid":"a3425f9c-e756-4880-b711-08f3c5d184e0","isSidechain":true,"agentId":"aa8d8d09b1b911247","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-5","id":"msg_011Ccshddv5DJWRAjxw9WzSQ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_015324ZrKybTtiqAx44nXsoH","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"C:\\Users\\brett\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\meterly-pipeline-test\\src\\api\\README.md","old_string":"- PUT `/v1/quotas`: `limit_per_window` is an integer `>= 1` (`<= 1e15`, BIGINT-safe); `customer_id`/`metric` reuse the same anchored allowlists as events; unknown fields (including a client-supplied `api_key_id`/`scope`) are rejected outright.","new_string":"- PUT `/v1/quotas`: `limit_per_window` is an integer `>= 1` (`<= 1e15`, BIGINT-safe); `customer_id`/`metric` reuse the same anchored allowlists as events; unknown fields (including a client-supplied `api_key_id`/`scope`) are rejected outright.\n- GET `/v1/quotas` accepts no body/query/path parameter (full, unpaginated list of the caller's tenant); DELETE `/v1/quotas` takes `customer_id`/`metric` as **query parameters** (`QuotaDeleteParams`), reusing PUT's exact same anchored allowlists; unknown query params (including a client-supplied `api_key_id`) are rejected outright."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1564,"cache_read_input_tokens":95502,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1564,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":3,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011Ccshdch9nhEwQg5pj1icc","attributionAgent":"documentation","type":"assistant","uuid":"43a8c2cc-d546-4004-9e97-e558050968a5","timestamp":"2026-07-10T03:54:39.534Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"C:\\Users\\brett\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\meterly-pipeline-test","sessionId":"cb1e5971-0f87-4706-9a1d-09f830df9e6f