{"parentUuid":"1a9b2d89-f311-46aa-8c62-cc70eb263df7","isSidechain":true,"agentId":"aa8d8d09b1b911247","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-5","id":"msg_011CcsheJFfbBdjWZhbBBXZS","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01HY1aGYyE93M2CB9tXMJSjb","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"C:\\Users\\brett\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\meterly-pipeline-test\\src\\services\\README.md","old_string":"- `quota_service` imports `src/repositories.quotas_repo` to upsert the cap.\n- All services receive an authenticated `AuthenticatedPrincipal` from the route handler (set by `require_api_key` guard); `principal.scope` gates `PUT /v1/quotas` at the route layer before `quota_service` ever runs (the export has no scope gate — any authenticated key may export its own tenant's data).","new_string":"- `quota_service` imports `src/repositories.quotas_repo` to upsert, list, and delete quota rows.\n- All services receive an authenticated `AuthenticatedPrincipal` from the route handler (set by `require_api_key` guard); `principal.scope` gates `PUT`/`GET`/`DELETE /v1/quotas` at the route layer (via the shared `_require_admin_and_throttled` dependency) before `quota_service` ever runs (the export has no scope gate — any authenticated key may export its own tenant's data)."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1141,"cache_read_input_tokens":97066,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1141,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":3,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null},"requestId":"req_011CcsheGbT9STueYcbHVCdW","attributionAgent":"documentation","type":"assistant","uuid":"301a1045-ec4c-4973-990b-bbeddb170bab","timestamp":"2026-07-10T03:54:52.029Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"C:\\Users\\brett\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\meterly-pipeline-test","sessionId