{"parentUuid":"94ed2e22-3a19-4f06-976d-0dd71718fdef","isSidechain":true,"promptId":"b6d534eb-f80d-405a-a05d-4c7eb6280654","agentId":"aa8d8d09b1b911247","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_0149Ao17Mhgx8GDCvneQt9zR","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# <Concise change title>\n2\t\n3\t> PR-description template → written to `.pipeline/pr-description.md`.\n4\t> The deployment gate requires this file to exist.\n5\t\n6\t## Summary\n7\t\n8\tOne paragraph: what changed and why. Link the plan: see `.pipeline/plan.md`\n9\t(includes the STRIDE threat model).\n10\t\n11\t## Changes\n12\t\n13\t- <Layer / area>: <what changed, one line each>\n14\t\n15\t## Decisions & tradeoffs\n16\t\n17\t- <Any non-obvious decision the reviewer should know, with the why>\n18\t\n19\t## Testing\n20\t\n21\t- Suites run and pass/fail summary from `.pipeline/test-results.json`.\n22\t- Combined coverage (lines / **branches** / functions) — call out the branch figure\n23\t  explicitly; note per-suite unit vs. integration when recorded.\n24\t- Test-pyramid shape: the `test_strategy` followed and the realized\n25\t  `tests_by_type` (unit / integration / e2e) counts.\n26\t- **Test quality** (advisory, from `.pipeline/test-quality.json` when present):\n27\t  mutation score over the changed core modules and the notable adversarial gaps\n28\t  (`what the tests do not catch`). Surface it for the reviewer; it does not gate.\n29\t\n30\t## Security\n31\t\n32\t- Scope (diff/full) and finding counts from `.pipeline/security-report.md`.\n33\t\n34\t## Supply chain\n35\t\n36\t- **Lockfile integrity:** dependency manifests and their lockfiles are in sync\n37\t  (from `lockfile-check.sh`); note any unpinned-dependency warnings.\n38\t- **SBOM:** whether a CycloneDX SBOM (`.pipeline/sbom.cdx.json`) was generated and\n39\t  its component count (best-effort; omit if Docker was unavailable).\n40\t\n41\t## Threat model\n42\t\n43\t- Reference the `## Threat Model` section of `.pipeline/plan.md`; call out any\n44\t  High-severity threat and its mitigation.\n45\t"}]},"uuid":"9b2a593f-b81f-484d-9c6a-5bd02053ca8b","timestamp":"2026-07-10T03:56:29.872Z","sourceToolAssistantUUID":"94ed2e22-3a19-4f06-976d-0dd71718fdef","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"C:\\Users\\brett\\OneDrive\\Documents\\GitHub\\meterly-pipeline-test","sessionId":"cb1e5971-0f87-4706-9a1d-09f830df9e6f","version":"2.1.205","gitBranch":"feature/quota-admin"}
